data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! BRAND NEW ROOF INSTALLED BEFORE CLOSING. ASK REALTOR FOR DETAILS. Welcome home! This charming three-bedroom, two-bathroom house is nestled in a picturesque and highly sought-after neighborhood. Prepare to be captivated by its attractive appeal and modern comforts. Step inside and be greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere. The open-concept layout ensures a seamless flow between the living, dining, and kitchen areas, making it perfect for entertaining friends and family. The abundant natural light flooding through large HURRICANE IMPACT WINDOWS creates an airy and cheerful ambiance throughout the day. The spacious kitchen boasts solid surface countertops, state-of-the-art appliances, and ample storage, making meal preparation a delightful experience. Tile and quality engineered wood laminate floors run throughout the home. The three well-appointed bedrooms provide a peaceful retreat after a long day. Each room offers plenty of space and closets to store your belongings neatly. The two modern bathrooms add to the convenience, designed with contemporary fixtures and finishes. Outside, you'll discover a private backyard oasis completely fenced in, and ideal for relaxation and outdoor gatherings. This home comes with a HOME WARRANTY Package – your key to worry-free homeownership! for your piece of mind. Embrace the serenity of the neighborhood while sipping your favorite beverage on the patio or tending to a lovely garden. Moreover, the location couldn't be more perfect. Enjoy the benefits of residing in a friendly community with excellent schools, parks, and recreational facilities nearby. Plus, you'll have easy access to various shopping and dining options, ensuring a vibrant and fulfilling lifestyle. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to call this lovely three-bedroom, two-bathroom house your home. Embrace the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience in this fantastic neighborhood. Make your move today and create cherished memories in this inviting home.
